{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act40side", "eventName": "相見歡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OR-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "金玉藏心", "storyInfo": "煌和行箸終於知道了彼此的身世。煌決定直接面見真龍，為所有人要一個說法。小大廚提起食盒，準備去見一位特殊的客人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g9_dalitemple", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞澄……你想要的，當年太師案的真相，就是這樣。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有什麼想問的？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說了這麼多，寧大人倒是隻字不提，自己在這一系列事件中的位置。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你為什麼要派人刺殺刑部尚書？", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞少卿不是已經有答案了嗎？許多年前，你不是指控我在亂局中為求自保，便派人謀害了查案的刑部尚書嗎？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧大人倒不必急著這樣抹黑自己。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#2$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實這個問題也困擾了我很久，顧筌時隔十幾年再回到百灶，為何偏偏留在你的家中？", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#2$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到那一次，我在你家看到那個女孩，我的最後一個問題才得到解答。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顧筌九死一生，還是要回到百灶，不只是為了查明當年真相，也是為了找到，自己遺落在百灶的女兒。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來顧筌告訴你的事，似乎也沒有那麼多。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，剩下的事，都只是我的猜想，要是有不對的地方，寧大人大可笑話我。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，當年太師背負謀逆之罪自盡後，舉國譁然，文武百官紛紛表態與太師割席。可是有一個學宮的學生，竟敢當眾上門憑弔太師。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也因此，他撞見了太師被抄家的場面。慌亂中，他只得帶走了太師家中一個出生不久的女嬰——巧的是，他自己的女兒也剛剛出世。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不知所措，帶著妻子和兩個嬰兒想要逃離百灶，可他不過是一個勢單力薄的書生，沒過多久，就被趕來的禁軍抓到。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概是那位禁軍心存恻隱，也是有意為太師保留血脈，放了那書生一條生路，帶回了那個書生的孩子。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知顧筌該作何想，不過當時的他大概也別無選擇。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個孩子落在刑部尚書手中，她的血脈一查便知，可如何處理這個本是局外人的孩子，反而成了懸而未決的難題。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這個時候，對於刑部尚書過激之舉早有不滿的寧大人，終於選擇鋌而走險，派人刺殺了刑部尚書。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太師案牽連甚廣，手上沾滿了血的刑部尚書遭人報復，似乎也在情理之中，時局既定，真龍便默許這一系列風波以這種方式落下帷幕。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那最後沒有解決的問題，也只剩下了那個孩子。從結果來看，她既然被寧大人收養，其中過程，似乎也不難猜。但要說目的……", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧大人，我沒記錯的話，你也在太師門下讀過書，對吧？", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……虞澄啊虞澄，你要是不在大理寺為官，你要是不在這獄中，我真不敢想，你這樣的心計，還能做出什麼事來。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可怕，真可怕……", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧大人過獎了，和顧筌比起來，我不過是個笨人。只是當這大理寺少卿，見過太多人了——見多了，也就懂了。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在想起來，顧筌在百珍宴上為真龍獻上那道菜，近乎求死之舉，實際上是已經與真相和解。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他在臨死前，沒有告訴我真相，卻向我透露了太師遺孤的下落——他是希望我查明真相後，也能選擇和解。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#3$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可我和解不了。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能用這種方式，找到那些留下的人、你在乎的人，逼你把真相吐出來。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧大人，細算來，你不能算是個壞人，或許只能算是懦弱……", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你大可恨我。", "name": "虞澄"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1617_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見到那個孩子一面，也算了了我一樁心願。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會去見陛下……", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g1_yusrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$midautumn", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……都知道了？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在剛剛……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還想問你——", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼……還能這麼冷靜……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是一個在心裡藏了很多年的猜想……終於被證實了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像紮在手心裡的一根刺，拔掉了，流了血，也就好了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼……不說話？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道……怎麼會是這樣……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該難過嗎？還是該生氣……？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道……我只是覺得腦子一團糟，心裡堵得難受……我不知道這一肚子火到底該向誰發洩！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，是不是該我反過來問你了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌……你能不能告訴我，顧筌……我的父親他，是個什麼樣的人？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他……他就是一個笨蛋、書呆子、說謊精！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我討厭說謊！我見過太多謊言，利欲薰心的謊言、懦弱的謊言、狡詐的謊言……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我真的沒見過……有人用一輩子去撒一個謊，還把自己的親女兒弄丟了，把自己也弄丟了，就為了保護一個毫不相干的人……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他怎麼……能這麼笨。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想起，以前在書上看過的一個故事……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從前有一個衛兵，守著江邊的一所驛站。有一天，他注意到上游發了洪水，想要跑到上游，去提醒那裡的人關閉水閘。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是他跑到一半，發現江水漲得太急，想要關閘已經來不及了，便想立刻趕回下游的村莊，讓那裡的人趕快疏散。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個人就這樣來回跑著，直到最後他也葬身在這場洪水裡，他什麼都沒能做到，誰也沒有救下……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又說這些繞來繞去的……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說……這個人做的事，聽起來是不是很熟悉？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白！雖然我搞不懂你說的繞來繞去的例子，但你在說他的壞話對不對？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不是個壞人！他只是……唉！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你當然有理由怨他，可是如果是他主動拋下了你，他又怎麼會花這麼多時間回來找你——", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼反而安慰起我來了……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌……你是感染者，對嗎？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你什麼時候知道——", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個人——是人精吧！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我沒有什麼別的意思……我只是在想，這其實本應該是我的命運……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在胡說八道什麼！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做錯了什麼事？有什麼厄運需要你承擔？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在活得沒什麼不好的，有許多夥伴，找到了自己的理想……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，明明你過得很慘吧！一個人生活在深宅大院裡，孤零零地長大就開心了？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼覺得，你像是在罵我……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是——", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白……我明白的。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啦……我還沒有問過，你到底叫什麼名字？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燭煌……顧燭煌，我爸——是他為我取的名字。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……我都忘了有多久沒和別人說過，我原來叫這個名字。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，這下我真的沒有秘密了。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“螢燭燭之煌，微明可顧”……真像是他會取的名字。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌……是不是到現在，我才算真正認識了你？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算……算是吧。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，我還有好多事沒跟你講，我還要帶你去維多利亞看看，我媽——應該說……你親生母親，你應該去見見她……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她還活著？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#7$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰告訴你她死了！她活得好好的，就在維多利亞西邊的一個小鎮裡。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等這邊的事結束了，我就帶你回去見她。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她……她一定很想見你……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……好好……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你哭什麼？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我沒有……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#8$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才是，你幹嘛也一副快要哭出來的表情……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#8$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是……高興。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我哪能想到，長這麼大了，我還能突然多一個妹妹。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡有這樣的姐妹……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#10$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說了，誰是妹妹還不一定呢。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#10$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我今天這麼難過，你就不能讓讓我？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛還安慰我來著……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#10$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是想說……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從今往後，你就不是孤零零的一個人了，對吧？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……真好啊。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世上百味，到底還是團圓的味道最好。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是……丟死人了，我跟著哭什麼……", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#11$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一樁心事，也算了啦。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，昨天晚上，在禁城中的那位大理寺的官員……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "驚蟄……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她送我出來的時候，被那個禁軍小姑娘截住了。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在該怎麼辦？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事，還沒結束……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去，把原本該做的事做完。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你打算做什麼？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為所有人……討一個說法。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一百年了。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於又回到了這裡——棋局開始的地方。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棋盤結網蒙塵，天元上還留有一顆黑子。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他伸手拂去了棋盤上的灰。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gintcrturvive", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g4_baizaomainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "y": 70.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$2", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上哪去？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫人送飯去。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你人走了，這店就不管了？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$2"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都什麼點了，早打烊了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$2"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天還開嗎？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……明天開不開，那得看明天的心情，說不準的。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#3$2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽你這意思，是要散夥了？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行啊，你還欠我半年工錢，結了帳就放你走。", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呿……怎麼這麼小氣！為你做了那麼多頓員工餐，就抵不過這幾個月的債了……", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#11$2"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行行行……廚房灶台右手邊，從牆角往外數第三塊磚，下面藏著我的最後一點零用錢。你拿去。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#14$2"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟了你不少年了。", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，整整十五年。在跟過我的那些秉燭人裡，你算時間最久的，說明我們還是蠻有緣的嘛，哈哈。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我一直記得我還是司歲台的秉燭人，恐怕也跟不了你這麼久。", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，說實話，我也很多年沒記起來我到底是誰了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是沒故意記得或者不記得，人也好獸也罷，就覺得這樣活著，有滋有味，沒什麼不好。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你最好永遠不要記起來。", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怕你想起來自己是誰，反而忘了人的口味。舌頭不好使了，這一手廚藝可就荒廢了。", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……我也不想啊。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#13$2"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我總還記得，家裡還有這些個不讓人放心的哥哥姐姐，他們也是要吃飯的。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況是最不讓人放心的那位……也不知道這麼久沒見，他到底怎麼樣了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道，今天去送了這一頓飯，是什麼後果？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……應該知道吧。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#4$2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像灶火邊上不能屯棉花，多自然的道理，司歲台當然不樂意讓我們開家庭聚會了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#4$2"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況是這個節骨眼上……搞不好要是打起來，明天你可能就見不到我了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#4$2"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#10$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……這些年，我做過許多飯，見了好多人。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想讓每一個走進這家店的客人，都能吃上好吃可口的飯，過的日子也都能圓滿。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "灶上的酸甜苦辣，心中的喜怒哀樂，世上的悲歡離合，多像同一回事啊。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#7$2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可鮮鱗多刺，海棠無香，世上多的還是遺憾。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#7$2"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肚子餓了要吃飯，睏了要睡覺……想念親人了，也總是要去見見的。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你就真的捨得……", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#10$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$2"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還有很多捨不得的東西，可是再捨不得，也不能一直緊抓著不放手啊。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$2"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老姜……我不在的時候，這家小飯館能暫時拜託給你嗎？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看著我做了那麼久的飯，我會做的菜，你應該也會個七七八八了吧。將來再有客人來，你就替我招呼招呼。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$2"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$2"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“餘味居”……這名字取得倒是蠻好。", "name": "餘"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$2"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這人間，餘味悠長啊。", "name": "餘"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#18$2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 70.0, "duration": 6.0, "ease": "OutQuad", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g7_forbiddencity", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 0.0, "duration": 6.0, "ease": "OutQuad", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1615_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1637_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1637_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告校將，巡防營派出全部兵力，已經在八個城區進行了一輪地毯式的搜查，還是沒發現目標。", "name": "巡邏的衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1637_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1615_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經過去一整天了……", "name": "“禁軍小教頭”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1615_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天亮之前，必須——", "name": "“禁軍小教頭”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1615_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說你在找我？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1615_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何人？！", "name": "“禁軍小教頭”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1615_1#8$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "